OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain cloudy in northwest Scotland
OL,7,Fwith some showery outbreaks of rain,
OL,8,Fbreezy here too. Drier elsewhere with
OL,9,Fclear spells for many and lighter
OL,10,Fwinds. A much fresher feeling night
OL,11,Fcompared to recent ones.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FDry with sunny spells for many
OL,14,Fof us on Monday. Scattered showers are
OL,15,Fpossible across the north, where it
OL,16,Fwill be breezy. Temperatures around
OL,17,Fthe seasonal average for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
